From Wikipedia: 

Amerigeddon is a 2016 American action film directed by Mike Norris and written by Gary Heavin. The movie describes a fictional attack on the United States by its own government, working in concert with a global terrorist organization and the United Nations. Heavin has said that he regards the events in the film as a "very real threat", and has described it as a movie that the government does not want people to see.

The movie was shot on Heavinâ€™s Central Texas ranch and in nearby towns, and the majority of the film's cast were recruited locally, Norris stating that "there were a number of agencies that would not allow their clients to be a part of the film".

The movie was released on 13 May 2016
